items.name: Enchanted Blurite Bolt
items.description: Blurite crossbow bolts tipped with enchanted Jade, that have a chance of dealing Earth magic damage and knocking your target down.

items.name: Enchanted Bronze Bolt
items.description: Bronze crossbow bolts tipped with enchanted opal, that have a chance to summon a lightning strike around your target, dealing Air magic damage to all nearby enemies.

items.name: Enchanted Iron Bolt
items.description: Iron crossbow bolts tipped with enchanted Jade, that have a chance of dealing Water magic damage and slowing your target.

items.name: Enchanted Steel Bolt
items.description: Steel crossbow bolts tipped with enchanted Red Topaz. Has a chance to create a necrotic bolt that heals your lifeward for a proportion of the damage dealt.

items.name: Iron Bolt
items.description: Crossbow Bolts made from Iron.

items.name: Steel Bolt
items.description: Crossbow Bolts made from Steel.

items.name: Purified King's Token
items.description: A ritually cleansed token containing a piece of another world.

items.name: Tainted King's Token
items.description: Proof of your victory over the garou king.

items.name: Challenge Horn
items.description: An ornate dragonkin horn, traditionally used to challenge someone to a duel of honour. Bring it to the dragonkin altar to challenge Velgar.

items.name: Challenge Horn Mouthpiece
items.description: The mouthpiece of the Challenge Horn, carved out of a dragon tooth.

items.name: Velgar's Head
items.description: Proof of your triumph over the Dragon General. It's dripping blood all over, you should probably get rid of it...

items.name: Dust-covered Sketchbook
items.description: A ruined notebook, buried beneath the earth.

items.name: Bandosian Amulet
items.description: A goblin amulet bearing the sigil of Bandos.

items.name: Druid's Bandosian Amulet
items.description: A goblin artefact, found on a druid.

items.name: Granite Maul Blueprints
items.description: The blueprints for an infamous weapon. Its individual components require special resources and Garou stonemasonry.

items.name: Imbued Granite Maul Head
items.description: A massive granite war hammer head. The Garou masons imbue their stone weapons with with Wild Anima to make them stronger than metal.

items.name: Imbued Leather Wrappings
items.description: Strips of imbued dire wolf leather for the granite maul grips. Infused with primal savagery.

items.name: Ornate Maul Handle
items.description: A carved piece of wood decorated with metal ornaments, sturdy enough to swing the heavy granite head. Made of blightwood, found in the Bloodblight Swamp.

items.name: Crystal Seed
items.description: A resonating crystal, waiting for the right song.

items.name: Mysterious Orb [Charged]
items.description: An orb obtained from a statue in the Magic Institute, charged with magical energy.

items.name: Mysterious Orb [Uncharged]
items.description: An orb obtained from a statue in the Magic Institute.

items.name: Ghostspeak Amulet
items.description: An amulet you found in a well in Brynmoor.

items.name: Primordial Heart
items.description: The heart of a nature spirit, you hunted this for Vannaka. He wants three of them.

items.name: Spectral Chinchompa Skull

items.name: Curse Fragment (Despair)
items.description: A crystallised part of a curse, imbued with Imaru's despair.

items.name: Curse Fragment (Grief)
items.description: A crystallised part of a curse, imbued with Imaru's grief.

items.name: Curse Fragment (Rage)
items.description: A crystallised part of a curse, imbued with Imaru's rage.

items.name: Imaru's Head
items.description: Proof of your triumph over the Soul-Eater. It's dripping ectoplasm all over, you should probably get rid of it...
